<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_52_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Paulus vns hat fürgelegt fraw Barbara des Caſpar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l5">wernicʒers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> elıche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan> von Jren vnd <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jrs</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l6">wirts wegen . vvie daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">hans </del> Jr dem hanſen hawgen von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l7">Pawcʒenvveẏler Jrem <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> . droet . Alſo daʒ Er vor ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l8">vnd den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnſicher ſeẏ . <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l9"><expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Armman<ex>n</ex></expan> ſichern wollet auf freuntlich reht / das </ab>
