<ab>Paulus von Mennheim von Seckendorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Paulus, uns hat fürgelegt fraw Barbara, des
                        Caspar Werniczers <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> eliche <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>, von
                        iren und <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>irs</expan> wirts wegen, wie daz ir dem Hansen Hawgen von
                        Pawczenweyler, irem <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, droet, also daz er vor
                        ew und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> unsicher sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> sichern wollet auf freuntlich reht. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>ir oder <expan>dhein<ex>er</ex></expan> der ewrn</add> czu
                                <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>cze sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        darümb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> euch dy
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> sleunigs
                            <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, wenn sie des ermant
                            <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und lat uns des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>freuntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen bey <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Egidii.</ab>
</div>
